<template>
  <v-container fluid>
    <PlanCardList />
    <PlanSelectList />
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import PlanCardList from '@/components/PlanCardList'
import PlanSelectList from '@/components/PlanSelectList'

export default {
  name: 'PlanView',
  components: {
    PlanCardList,
    PlanSelectList,
  },
  mounted() {
    this.getPlans()
    document.title = 'Home | Digital Wave'
  },
  methods: {
    async getPlans() {
      await axios
        .get('api/v1/plans/')
        .then(response => {
          this.plans = response.data
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.log(error)
        })
    },
  }
}
</script>
